Shervin Kalkhoran


  Updating OS
1. scp ESXi670-201811001.zip root@10.12.17.:/vmfs/volumes/datastore1
2. ssh root@10.12.17.
3. cd /vmfs/volumes/datastore1
4. esxcli software profile update -d /vmfs/volumes/datastore1/ESXi670-201811001.zip -p $(esxcli software sources profile list -d /vmfs/volumes/datastore1/ESXi670-201113001.zip | awk '{ print $1 }' | tail -n 1)
5. rm ESXi670-201811001.zip

  Installing LSI
1. scp lsi-mr3-7.705.09.00-1OEM.670.0.0.8169922.x86_64.vib root@10.12.17.:/vmfs/volumes/datastore1/
2. ssh root@10.12.17.
3. esxcli software vib install -v /vmfs/volumes/datastore1/lsi-mr3-7.705.09.00-1OEM.670.0.0.8169922.x86_64.vib
4. rm /vmfs/volumes/datastore1/lsi-mr3-7.705.09.00-1OEM.670.0.0.8169922.x86_64.vib


file location for the OS update file
ftp://10.12.17.15/pub/iso/esxi/6/

file location for the LSI driver 
ftp://10.12.17.15/pub/software/raid/esxi/
